</div><div class="courseblock">
<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>FIN&#160;320.  Managerial Finance.  3 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Short-term asset management, capital budgeting under certainty and uncertainty, capital structure and dividend policy, valuation and risk, capital asset prices, financial policy for firms. Course Information: Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=FIN%20300" title="FIN&#160;300" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'FIN 300');">FIN&#160;300</a>; or <a href="/search/?P=FIN%20301" title="FIN&#160;301" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'FIN 301');">FIN&#160;301</a> and <a href="/search/?P=FIN%20302" title="FIN&#160;302" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'FIN 302');">FIN&#160;302</a>.<br />
