<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>FIN&#160;412.  Portfolio Management.  3 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Development of portfolio theory; establishment of portfolio objectives for individuals, corporations, banks, pension and mutual funds; evaluation of portfolio performance. Course Information: Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=FIN%20310" title="FIN&#160;310" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'FIN 310');">FIN&#160;310</a>.<br />
